cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with tracking objects in videos based on language queries, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a framework that involves machine learning (ML) models for prediction, which falls under cs.AI. Additionally, the paper discusses the integration of different sub-tasks, which is related to optimization and decision-making, falling under cs.LG. Finally, the paper benchmarks its framework on video datasets, which falls under cs.MM.
